  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2745409/" class="title-link">林夕的香港与香港的林夕</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2745409"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2582608/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2582608-92.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2582608/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">丁卵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-11-13"
      class="main-meta">2009-11-13 08:55:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2745409_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        算上这本《我所爱的香港》，林夕在内地已出满了三本书。但与《原来你非不快乐》、《曾经》相比，《我所爱的香港》落在了一个实处，更得人所爱，也更让人有所思省。     香港地窄人挤，摩天大楼鳞次栉比，生活其间须有强大的心理，但环境作用于人，到底不是谁都能受得了的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2745409/#comments">(13回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">108有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
